data.description: REMARKABLE character filled 2361 sq ft 3 bed, 2 full bath with amazing custom storage cabinetry and hardwood floors throughout, 2 fireplaces, main floor master, 1st floor laundry, fenced in backyard, custom patio, and Ruihley Park across the street. The 27x25 great room boasts beautiful cathedral ceilings and cozy fireplace feels like a retreat! Recent updates 2022 Roof, 2022 Furnace and A/C units, 17 new light fixtures, bathroom flooring, custom ceramic kitchen backsplash, battery back-up and sump pump and so much more! You absolutely don't want to miss out on this one!
